<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Many stands are open and lack continuous fuel for fires; however, stands invaded by <i>Bromus tectorum </i>easily burn. <i>Sarcobatus vermiculatus </i>readily sprouts after low-intensity burns, and seeds easily disburse into recently burned areas from unburned shrubs (Anderson 2004b). Fire characteristics are little known for this alliance.</div>
